From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000000 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: The Managarm Project <info@managarm.org>
Date: Thu, 5 Jun 2026 00:00:00 +0200
Subject: [PATCH] build: recognize managarm as a Linux-like target

Map *-managarm-* triples to a GNU/Linux-like OS and a Linux kernel so the
GTK3 toolkit and unix build paths are selected.
---
--- a/build/moz.configure/init.configure
+++ b/build/moz.configure/init.configure
@@ -485,6 +485,9 @@
     if "android" in os:
         canonical_os = "Android"
         canonical_kernel = "Linux"
+    elif "managarm" in os:
+        canonical_os = "GNU"
+        canonical_kernel = "Linux"
     elif os.startswith("linux"):
         canonical_os = "GNU"
         canonical_kernel = "Linux"
